channel.title: Tracks I don’t know where to go with [WIP]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I’ve got some projects I think could have good potential but I don’t know where to go with them, I’m open to collab on them if anyone wants to, they are all three very different styles.
Bitcrushed/techno thingy:
https://app.auxy.co/projects/GPL-Ck2VWy9sTg_MmkrqwQ==
Trap/rap beat with vocal chops:
https://app.auxy.co/projects/bs5BDW5074NdRXIjR4cdsQ==
Some psychedelic chords:
https://app.auxy.co/projects/dW_cAQLvJcGm-ElGRMyp-Q==
I haven’t made any full tracks in a while so I’m hoping to get back in the swing of things with these.
